Interface SkinModel

All Superinterfaces:
ListModel, Locator, Model, ResourceLocator
public SkinModel
extends ListModel, ResourceLocator

Interface for a skin model. This list model describes a list of skin objects.

The skin model supports the following strategies:

  • ListLoadAheadStrategy
  • HiddenMetaDataLoadingStrategy
